..TEXT:
|Vero @e~: The phrase indicates something to be
wondered at (cf. English "verily") -- that the poet has been
mysteriously transported across Acheron while he was in a deep
sleep.  Such miraculous happenings will not continue; instead,
the normal or natural conditions of the real world will prevail
in the otherworld.
..TCHR:
