..TEXT:
|porta~: Many MSS read ^parte.~  Petrocchi in his
vol. I, ^Introduzione~, pp. 170-71, notes other references to
baptism as the door of faith.  Among others, he cites Augustine,
^conf.~ XIII, 21: "Non enim intratur aliter in regno caelorum ex
illo."  ("For there is entrance into the kingdom of heaven no
other way.")
