|Poi...filosofica famiglia~: Two groups have
been seen so far: poets, represented by the four who came forward
to greet Virgil; and warriors, represented -- with the exception of
Saladin -- by those who had a part in the founding of the Roman
Empire.  Now the wayfarer raises his eyes to see a third group:
philosophers, with Aristotle sitting highest.
